# Final Project 8

## Project Overview

This project builds a containerized R Markdown report using Docker.  
The report is generated automatically from the project files and saved to a local folder.

---

## Files

- `Dockerfile` – defines the Docker image
- `Makefile` – shortcuts for building image and generating report
- `report.Rmd` – source report
- `code/` – analysis scripts
- `data/` – input data
- `report/` – generated output report

---

## How to Build the Docker Image

To build the Docker image, run:

```bash
make build